OL,5,G0100 Outback Truckers
OL,6,     FSteve and dog Bella are in a race
OL,7,     Facross the red deserts of
OL,8,     FAustralia hauling classic cars to
OL,9,     Fauction but delays in loading and
OL,10,     Fthe arrival of the wet season
OL,11,     Fthreaten the journey home.
OL,12,G0200 Trucking Hell
OL,13,     FThere's an emergency in East
OL,14,     FLondon when a 25-ton truck hits a
OL,15,     Frailway bridge. And Buzz needs to
OL,16,     Fco-ordinate a multi-agency
OL,17,     Ftaskforce when a refrigerated
OL,18,     Florry catches fire on the A42.
